						<summary>

						<p>Slab paved on the platform round the <hi rend="italic">Dhvajastaṁbha</hi> of the Kēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>This undated epigraph may be assigned to the 8th century, on the basis of palaeography and internal evidence.</p>						

						<p>It registers a gift of land as <hi rend="italic">Panavīsa</hi> by Balavarmarāju to Chiḷkapaṟa at Koṟapaṟu.</p>						

						</summary>
